                    ***  Quick Install Instructions! ***

Unzip this archive into a temporary directory.

Type SETUP

The door files will be copied to the correct directories, then
the BRAINSET program will run. You will asked for specific setup info
for the door.

   * FAILURE TO INSTALL BY THE ABOVE METHOD WILL CAUSE THE DOOR TO FAIL *

       * DO NOT COPY THE FILES YOURSELF, LET THE SETUP.BAT DO IT! *

If you are updating from a previous version, you will be asked if you wish
to overwrite all or some files. Be sure you do not overwrite customized
menu screens.

If you get a BAD COMMAND OR FILENAME notice from DOS, this means that
the BRAINEX DOOR MANAGER was not properly installed.

